#: panels/color/cc-color-panel.ui:4 panels/wacom/calibrator/calibrator.blp:39
msgid "Screen Calibration"
msgstr "ການ​ປັບ​ທຽບ​ໜ້າ​ຈໍ"

#: panels/color/cc-color-panel.ui:12
msgid "Calibration Quality"
msgstr "ຄຸນ​ນະ​ພາບ​ການ​ປັບ​ທຽບ"

#: panels/color/cc-color-panel.ui:21
msgid ""
"Calibration will produce a profile that you can use to color manage your "
"screen. The longer you spend on calibration, the better the quality of the "
"color profile."
msgstr "ການ​ປັບ​ທຽບ​ຈະ​ສ້າງ​ໂປ​ຣ​ໄຟລ໌​ທີ່​ທ່ານ​ສາ​ມາດ​ໃຊ້​ເພື່ອ​ຈັດ​ການ​ສີ​ຂອງ​ໜ້າ​ຈໍ​ຂອງ​ທ່ານ. ຍິ່ງ​ໃຊ້​ເວ​ລາ​ໃນ​ການ​ປັບ​ທຽບ​ດົນ​ເທົ່າ​ໃດ, ຄຸນ​ນະ​ພາບ​ຂອງ​ໂປ​ຣ​ໄຟລ໌​ສີ​ກໍ​ຈະ​ດີ​ຂຶ້ນ​ເທົ່າ​ນັ້ນ."

#: panels/color/cc-color-panel.ui:28
msgid "You will not be able to use your device while calibration takes place."
msgstr "ທ່ານ​ຈະ​ບໍ່​ສາ​ມາດ​ໃຊ້​ອຸ​ປະ​ກອນ​ຂອງ​ທ່ານ​ໄດ້ ໃນ​ຂະ​ນະ​ທີ່​ກຳ​ລັງ​ປັບ​ທຽບ."

#. This is the approximate time it takes to calibrate the display.
#: panels/color/cc-color-panel.ui:40
msgid "Quality"
msgstr "ຄຸນ​ນະ​ພາບ"

#. This is the approximate time it takes to calibrate the display.
#: panels/color/cc-color-panel.ui:51
msgid "Approximate Time"
msgstr "ເວ​ລາ​ໂດຍ​ປະ​ມານ"

#: panels/color/cc-color-panel.ui:82
msgid "Calibration Device"
msgstr "ອຸ​ປະ​ກອນ​ປັບ​ທຽບ"

#: panels/color/cc-color-panel.ui:90
msgid "Select the sensor device you want to use for calibration."
msgstr "ເລືອກ​ອຸ​ປະ​ກອນ​ເຊັນ​ເຊີ​ທີ່​ທ່ານ​ຕ້ອງ​ການ​ໃຊ້​ສຳ​ລັບ​ການ​ປັບ​ທຽບ."

#: panels/color/cc-color-panel.ui:117
msgid "Display Type"
msgstr "ປະ​ເພດ​ຈໍ​ສະ​ແດງ​ຜົນ"

#: panels/color/cc-color-panel.ui:125
msgid "Select the type of display that is connected."
msgstr "ເລືອກ​ປະ​ເພດ​ຈໍ​ສະ​ແດງ​ຜົນ​ທີ່​ເຊື່ອມ​ຕໍ່​ຢູ່."

#: panels/color/cc-color-panel.ui:152
msgid "Profile Whitepoint"
msgstr "ຈຸດ​ສີ​ຂາວ​ຂອງ​ໂປ​ຣ​ໄຟລ໌"

#: panels/color/cc-color-panel.ui:160
msgid ""
"Select a display target white point. Most displays should be calibrated to a "
"D65 illuminant."
msgstr "ເລືອກ​ຈຸດ​ສີ​ຂາວ​ເປົ້າ​ໝາຍ​ຂອງ​ຈໍ​ສະ​ແດງ​ຜົນ. ຈໍ​ສະ​ແດງ​ຜົນ​ສ່ວນ​ໃຫຍ່​ຄວນ​ຖືກ​ປັບ​ທຽບ​ກັບ​ແສງ​ D65."

#: panels/color/cc-color-panel.ui:187
msgid "Display Brightness"
msgstr "ຄວາມ​ສະ​ຫວ່າງ​ຂອງ​ຈໍ​ສະ​ແດງ​ຜົນ"

#: panels/color/cc-color-panel.ui:195
msgid ""
"Please set the display to a brightness that is typical for you. Color "
"management will be most accurate at this brightness level."
msgstr "ກະ​ລຸ​ນາ​ຕັ້ງ​ຄ່າ​ຄວາມ​ສະ​ຫວ່າງ​ຂອງ​ຈໍ​ສະ​ແດງ​ຜົນ​ໃຫ້​ເປັນ​ລະ​ດັບ​ທີ່​ທ່ານ​ໃຊ້​ເປັນ​ປົກ​ກະ​ຕິ. ການ​ຈັດ​ການ​ສີ​ຈະ​ມີ​ຄວາມ​ແມ້ນ​ຢຳ​ທີ່​ສຸດ​ໃນ​ລະ​ດັບ​ຄວາມ​ສະ​ຫວ່າງ​ນີ້."

#: panels/color/cc-color-panel.ui:202
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can use the brightness level used with one of the other "
"profiles for this device."
msgstr "ອີກ​ທາງ​ເລືອກ​ໜຶ່ງ, ທ່ານ​ສາ​ມາດ​ໃຊ້​ລະ​ດັບ​ຄວາມ​ສະ​ຫວ່າງ​ທີ່​ໃຊ້​ກັບ​ໂປ​ຣ​ໄຟລ໌​ອື່ນໆ​ສຳ​ລັບ​ອຸ​ປະ​ກອນ​ນີ້."

#: panels/color/cc-color-panel.ui:214
msgid "Profile Name"
msgstr "ຊື່​ໂປ​ຣ​ໄຟລ໌"

#: panels/color/cc-color-panel.ui:222
msgid ""
"You can use a color profile on different devices, or even create profiles "
"for different lighting conditions."
msgstr "ທ່ານ​ສາ​ມາດ​ໃຊ້​ໂປ​ຣ​ໄຟລ໌​ສີ​ໃນ​ອຸ​ປະ​ກອນ​ຕ່າງໆ, ຫຼື​ແມ້​ກະ​ທັ້ງ​ສ້າງ​ໂປ​ຣ​ໄຟລ໌​ສຳ​ລັບ​ສະ​ພາບ​ແສງ​ທີ່​ແຕກ​ຕ່າງ​ກັນ."

#: panels/color/cc-color-panel.ui:229
msgid "Profile Name:"
msgstr "ຊື່​ໂປ​ຣ​ໄຟລ໌:"

