#: panels/privacy/diagnostics/cc-diagnostics-page.c:125
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Sending reports of technical problems helps us improve %s. Reports are sent "
"anonymously and are scrubbed of personal data — %s."
msgstr "ການສົ່ງລາຍງານບັນຫາທາງເທັກນິກຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ພວກເຮົາປັບປຸງ %s ໄດ້. ລາຍງານຈະຖືກສົ່ງໂດຍບໍ່ລະບຸຕົວຕົນ ແລະ ຈະຖືກລຶບຂໍ້ມູນສ່ວນຕົວອອກ — %s."

#. translators: The '%s' is the distributor's name, such as 'Fedora'
#: panels/privacy/diagnostics/cc-diagnostics-page.c:130
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Sending reports of technical problems helps us improve %s. Reports are sent "
"anonymously and are scrubbed of personal data."
msgstr "ການສົ່ງລາຍງານບັນຫາທາງເທັກນິກຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ພວກເຮົາປັບປຸງ %s ໄດ້. ລາຍງານຈະຖືກສົ່ງໂດຍບໍ່ລະບຸຕົວຕົນ ແລະ ຈະຖືກລຶບຂໍ້ມູນສ່ວນຕົວອອກ."

#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-boot-dialog.blp:47
msgid ""
"Secure boot prevents malicious software from being loaded when the device "
"starts.\n"
"\n"
"For more information, contact the hardware manufacturer or IT support."
msgstr "ການບູດແບບປອດໄພປ້ອງກັນບໍ່ໃຫ້ຊັອບແວທີ່ເປັນອັນຕະລາຍຖືກໂຫຼດຂຶ້ນມາເມື່ອອຸປະກອນເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ.\n\nສຳລັບຂໍ້ມູນເພີ່ມເຕີມ, ຕິດຕໍ່ຜູ້ຜະລິດຮາດແວ ຫຼື ຜູ້ຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອດ້ານ IT."

#. TRANSLATORS: secure boot refers to the system firmware security mode
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-boot-dialog.c:71
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-page.c:122
msgid "Secure Boot is Active"
msgstr "ການບູດແບບປອດໄພກຳລັງເຮັດວຽກ"

#. TRANSLATORS: this is the first section of the decription
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-boot-dialog.c:76
msgid ""
"Secure boot prevents malicious software from being loaded when the device "
"starts. It is currently turned on and is functioning correctly."
msgstr "ການບູດແບບປອດໄພປ້ອງກັນບໍ່ໃຫ້ຊັອບແວທີ່ເປັນອັນຕະລາຍຖືກໂຫຼດຂຶ້ນມາເມື່ອອຸປະກອນເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ. ປັດຈຸບັນມັນເປີດຢູ່ ແລະ ເຮັດວຽກຢ່າງຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#. TRANSLATORS: secure boot refers to the system firmware security mode
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-boot-dialog.c:82
msgid "Secure Boot Has Problems"
msgstr "ການບູດແບບປອດໄພມີບັນຫາ"

#. TRANSLATORS: this is the first section of the decription.
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-boot-dialog.c:86
msgid ""
"Secure boot prevents malicious software from being loaded when the device "
"starts. It is currently turned on, but will not work due to having an "
"invalid key."
msgstr "ການບູດແບບປອດໄພປ້ອງກັນບໍ່ໃຫ້ຊັອບແວທີ່ເປັນອັນຕະລາຍຖືກໂຫຼດຂຶ້ນມາເມື່ອອຸປະກອນເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ. ປັດຈຸບັນມັນເປີດຢູ່, ແຕ່ຈະບໍ່ເຮັດວຽກຍ້ອນມີກະແຈທີ່ບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#. TRANSLATORS: this is the second section of description.
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-boot-dialog.c:89
msgid ""
"Secure boot problems can often be resolved from your device's UEFI firmware "
"settings (BIOS) and your hardware manufacturer may provide information on "
"how to do this."
msgstr "ບັນຫາການບູດແບບປອດໄພມັກຈະສາມາດແກ້ໄຂໄດ້ຈາກການຕັ້ງຄ່າເຟີມແວ UEFI (BIOS) ຂອງອຸປະກອນຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ ຜູ້ຜະລິດຮາດແວຂອງທ່ານອາດຈະໃຫ້ຂໍ້ມູນກ່ຽວກັບວິທີການເຮັດສິ່ງນີ້."

#. TRANSLATORS: this is the third section of description.
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-boot-dialog.c:92
msgid "For help, contact your hardware manufacturer or IT support provider."
msgstr "ສຳລັບການຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອ, ຕິດຕໍ່ຜູ້ຜະລິດຮາດແວຂອງທ່ານ ຫຼື ຜູ້ໃຫ້ບໍລິການຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອດ້ານ IT."

#. TRANSLATORS: secure boot refers to the system firmware security mode
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-boot-dialog.c:98
msgid "Secure Boot is Turned Off"
msgstr "ການບູດແບບປອດໄພປິດຢູ່"

#. TRANSLATORS: this is the first section of the description.
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-boot-dialog.c:102
msgid ""
"Secure boot prevents malicious software from being loaded when the device "
"starts. It is currently turned off."
msgstr "ການບູດແບບປອດໄພປ້ອງກັນບໍ່ໃຫ້ຊັອບແວທີ່ເປັນອັນຕະລາຍຖືກໂຫຼດຂຶ້ນມາເມື່ອອຸປະກອນເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ. ປັດຈຸບັນມັນປິດຢູ່."

#. TRANSLATORS: this is the second section of the description.
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-boot-dialog.c:105
msgid ""
"Secure boot can often be turned on from your device's UEFI firmware settings "
"(BIOS). For help, contact your hardware manufacturer or IT support provider."
msgstr "ການບູດແບບປອດໄພມັກຈະສາມາດເປີດໄດ້ຈາກການຕັ້ງຄ່າເຟີມແວ UEFI (BIOS) ຂອງອຸປະກອນຂອງທ່ານ. ສຳລັບການຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອ, ຕິດຕໍ່ຜູ້ຜະລິດຮາດແວຂອງທ່ານ ຫຼື ຜູ້ໃຫ້ບໍລິການຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອດ້ານ IT."

#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-dialog.blp:54
msgid "_Copy Technical Report"
msgstr "_ສຳເນົາລາຍງານທາງເທັກນິກ"

#. TRANSLATORS: in reference to firmware protection: 0/4 stars
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-dialog.c:108
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-page.c:532
msgid "Security Checks Failed"
msgstr "ການກວດສອບຄວາມປອດໄພລົ້ມເຫຼວ"

#. TRANSLATORS: This is the description to describe the failure on
#. checking the security items.
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-dialog.c:111
msgid ""
"Hardware does not pass checks. This means that you are not protected against "
"common hardware security issues.\n"
"\n"
"It may be possible to resolve hardware security issues by updating your "
"firmware or changing device configuration options. However, failures can "
"stem from the physical hardware itself and may not be fixable."
msgstr "ຮາດແວບໍ່ຜ່ານການກວດສອບ. ນີ້ໝາຍຄວາມວ່າທ່ານບໍ່ໄດ້ຮັບການປົກປ້ອງຈາກບັນຫາຄວາມປອດໄພຮາດແວທົ່ວໄປ.\n\nອາດເປັນໄປໄດ້ທີ່ຈະແກ້ໄຂບັນຫາຄວາມປອດໄພຮາດແວໂດຍການອັບເດດເຟີມແວຂອງທ່ານ ຫຼື ປ່ຽນຕົວເລືອກການຕັ້ງຄ່າອຸປະກອນ. ແນວໃດກໍ່ຕາມ, ຄວາມລົ້ມເຫຼວອາດເກີດຈາກຕົວຮາດແວເອງ ແລະ ອາດຈະບໍ່ສາມາດແກ້ໄຂໄດ້."

#. TRANSLATORS: in reference to firmware protection: 1/4 stars
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-dialog.c:121
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-page.c:539
msgid "Basic Security Checks Passed"
msgstr "ຜ່ານການກວດສອບຄວາມປອດໄພຂັ້ນພື້ນຖານ"

#. TRANSLATORS: This description describes the device passing the
#. minimum requirement of security check.
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-dialog.c:124
msgid ""
"This device meets basic security requirements and has protection against "
"some hardware security threats. However, it lacks other recommended "
"protections."
msgstr "ອຸປະກອນນີ້ຜ່ານຂໍ້ກຳນົດຄວາມປອດໄພຂັ້ນພື້ນຖານ ແລະ ມີການປົກປ້ອງຈາກໄພຄຸກຄາມຄວາມປອດໄພຮາດແວບາງຢ່າງ. ແນວໃດກໍ່ຕາມ, ມັນຂາດການປົກປ້ອງອື່ນໆທີ່ແນະນຳ."

#. TRANSLATORS: in reference to firmware protection: 2~4 stars
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-dialog.c:134
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-page.c:549
msgid "Protected"
msgstr "ປອດໄພ"

#. TRANSLATOR: This description describes the devices passing
#. the extended security check.
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-dialog.c:137
msgid ""
"This device passes current security tests. It is protected against the "
"majority of hardware security threats."
msgstr "ອຸປະກອນນີ້ຜ່ານການທົດສອບຄວາມປອດໄພໃນປັດຈຸບັນ. ມັນໄດ້ຮັບການປົກປ້ອງຈາກໄພຄຸກຄາມຄວາມປອດໄພຮາດແວສ່ວນໃຫຍ່."

#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-dialog.c:144
msgid "Checks Unavailable"
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດກວດສອບໄດ້"

#. TRANSLATORS: When the security result is unavailable, this description is shown.
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-dialog.c:146
msgid ""
"Device security checks are not available for this device. It is not possible "
"to tell whether it meets hardware security requirements."
msgstr "ການກວດສອບຄວາມປອດໄພຂອງອຸປະກອນບໍ່ສາມາດໃຊ້ໄດ້ກັບອຸປະກອນນີ້. ບໍ່ສາມາດບອກໄດ້ວ່າມັນຜ່ານຂໍ້ກຳນົດຄວາມປອດໄພຮາດແວຫຼືບໍ່."

#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-dialog.c:366
msgid "Report copied to clipboard"
msgstr "ສຳເນົາລາຍງານໄປທີ່ຄລິບບອດແລ້ວ"

#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-help-dialog.blp:5
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-page.blp:13
msgid "About Device Security"
msgstr "ກ່ຽວກັບຄວາມປອດໄພຂອງອຸປະກອນ"

#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-help-dialog.blp:28
msgid ""
"Device security provides information about how protected your device is "
"against security issues which target the hardware itself.\n"
"\n"
"Aspects of hardware that affect security include:\n"
"\n"
"• security features that are built into a hardware itself;\n"
"• how the hardware is configured to protect against security issues;\n"
"• the security of the software runs directly on the hardware.\n"
"\n"
"Security threats which affect hardware include malware and viruses that "
"target the software that runs directly on the hardware. It also includes "
"physical tampering, such as physical connection to the hardware to read data "
"and implant malware.\n"
"\n"
"Device security is just one aspect of security, and does not reflect the "
"overall security status of the system and applications."
msgstr "ຄວາມປອດໄພຂອງອຸປະກອນໃຫ້ຂໍ້ມູນກ່ຽວກັບວ່າອຸປະກອນຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ຮັບການປົກປ້ອງຈາກບັນຫາຄວາມປອດໄພທີ່ແນໃສ່ຕົວຮາດແວເອງໄດ້ດີສໍ່າໃດ.\n\nດ້ານຕ່າງໆຂອງຮາດແວທີ່ສົ່ງຜົນກະທົບຕໍ່ຄວາມປອດໄພລວມມີ:\n\n• ຄຸນສົມບັດຄວາມປອດໄພທີ່ສ້າງຂຶ້ນໃນຕົວຮາດແວເອງ;\n• ວິທີທີ່ຮາດແວຖືກຕັ້ງຄ່າເພື່ອປົກປ້ອງຈາກບັນຫາຄວາມປອດໄພ;\n• ຄວາມປອດໄພຂອງຊັອບແວທີ່ເຮັດວຽກໂດຍກົງເທິງຮາດແວ.\n\nໄພຄຸກຄາມຄວາມປອດໄພທີ່ສົ່ງຜົນກະທົບຕໍ່ຮາດແວລວມມີມັລແວ ແລະ ໄວຣັສທີ່ແນໃສ່ຊັອບແວທີ່ເຮັດວຽກໂດຍກົງເທິງຮາດແວ. ມັນຍັງລວມເຖິງການລ່ວງລະເມີດທາງກາຍະພາບ, ເຊັ່ນ ການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ທາງກາຍະພາບກັບຮາດແວເພື່ອອ່ານຂໍ້ມູນ ແລະ ຝັງມັລແວ.\n\nຄວາມປອດໄພຂອງອຸປະກອນເປັນພຽງດ້ານໜຶ່ງຂອງຄວາມປອດໄພ, ແລະ ບໍ່ໄດ້ສະທ້ອນເຖິງສະຖານະຄວາມປອດໄພໂດຍລວມຂອງລະບົບ ແລະ ແອັບພລິເຄຊັນ."

#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-page.blp:5
msgid "Device Security"
msgstr "ຄວາມປອດໄພຂອງອຸປະກອນ"

#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-page.blp:36
