msgstr "ຄວາມປອດໄພຂອງອຸປະກອນບໍ່ສາມາດໃຊ້ໄດ້"

#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-page.blp:38
msgid ""
"Device Security is only available on physical hardware. No physical hardware "
"has been detected."
msgstr "ຄວາມປອດໄພຂອງອຸປະກອນສາມາດໃຊ້ໄດ້ກັບຮາດແວຈິງເທົ່ານັ້ນ. ບໍ່ພົບຮາດແວຈິງ."

#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-page.blp:160
msgid "Security Events"
